def model_f(phi):
    return 4 * phi**3 - 3 * phi**4

delta = 0.001

def eps_old(phi):
    return 1 / (delta + model_f(phi))

def eps_u_old(x):
    return x / (delta + x)

def eps_new(phi, pwr):
    return 1 / delta + 1 - 1 / delta * eps_u(model_f(phi), pwr)

def eps_u(x, pwr):
    return 1 - (1 - delta) * (1 - x)**pwr + delta * (x - 1)

In[17]:
eps_0 = 2.6 * 8.85e-12
Gamma = 2.6 * 3.12228e-10

def model_f_phi(phi):
    return 12.0 * phi * phi * (1.0 - phi)

def eps_u_x(x, pwr):
    return delta + (1.0 - delta) * pwr * (1.0 - x)**(pwr - 1)

def eps_new_phi(phi, pwr):
	return -eps_0 / delta * eps_u_x(model_f(phi), pwr) * model_f_phi(phi)

def eps_old_phi(phi):
	return -eps_0 / (model_f(phi) + delta)**2 * model_f_phi(phi)

def right_side_old(phi, params):
    return \
        0.5 * eps_old_phi(phi) * params['Phi_gradient']**2 + \
        Gamma / params['l']**2 * model_f_phi(phi)

def right_side_new(phi, params):
    return \
        0.5 * eps_new_phi(phi, params['pwr']) * params['Phi_gradient']**2 + \
        Gamma / params['l']**2 * model_f_phi(phi)
In[18]:
def right_side_plot(model, times, right_side):
    plt.figure(figsize=(9, 6))
    plt.xlabel(r'$x$')
    plt.ylabel(r'$F\'(\phi)$')
    t_indices = [model.t_index(t) for t in times]
    for i in t_indices:
        plt.plot(model.xs, right_side(model.phi[i], model.params))
    plt.legend(['$t = {:.3e}$'.format(model.ts[i]) for i in t_indices],
        bbox_to_anchor=(1.02, 1), loc="upper left")
    plt.show()

In[20]:
def t_F_max(model, right_side):
    t_index = right_side(
        model.df_phi,
        model.params
    ).abs().max(axis=1).argmax()
    return model.ts[t_index], right_side(model.phi[t_index], model.params).abs().max()

def right_side_plot_parts(model, times, right_side_parts):
    plt.figure(figsize=(9, 6))
    plt.xlabel(r'$x$')
    plt.ylabel(r'$F\'(\phi)$')
    t_indices = [model.t_index(t) for t in times]
    for j, i in enumerate(t_indices):
        part_1, part_2 = right_side_parts(model.phi[i], model.params)
        plt.plot(model.xs, part_2, color='C' + str(j))
        #plt.plot(model.xs, part_2, '--', color='C' + str(j), label='_nolegend_')
    plt.legend(['$t = {:.3e}$'.format(model.ts[i]) for i in t_indices],
        bbox_to_anchor=(1.02, 1), loc="upper left")
    plt.show()
